zzapper wrote:
> BTW what's the best way to reload/unload a shell function you are working on?

I've had this function for ages.

reload() {
  if (( $# == 0 )); then
    print "Reload what?" >&2
    return 1
  fi

  while (( $# )); do
    unfunction $1 && autoload $1
    shift
  done
}

